    <p>Master of Music Anna Näkkäläjärvi has been appointed as deputy for the Cultural Secretary. Näkkäläjärvi will begin her work on 18 May in the Saami Parliaments General office in Inari.</p>
    <p>Further information from Executive Director Juha Guttorm.</p>
